{"tid":1417563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］口號調整關乎整個社運成敗","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:59.000Z","uid":294715,"like":23,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"191a743725f4fb22a70e992a6458518eeb94541f","tid":1417563,"uid":294715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:48:39.000Z","msg":"我係P牌仔 大家咪屌住<br />\n<br />\n我今日睇左劉細良城寨（片link擺下面）<br />\n我都係覆述簡化為主 詳細懇請大家自己睇片<br />\n事關<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林奠8月5號早上記招開始意圖將反送中運動同港獨掛勾</span></span><br />\n試圖為送中畫上句號 將焦點轉移令自己立於不敗之地<br />\n而主要備受爭議就係近期遊行口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n細良提到呢個口號並無實質內容 而且好多市民未必有推翻政權嘅思想 其實唔屬於革命<br />\n所以懇請大家 另覓口號 小弟暫時未有想法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但係一定要改口 否則隨時收皮</span></span><br />\n大家請集思廣益 甚至其實重申5大訴求嘅口號都好<br />\n革命嘅字眼真係可面則免 比位林奠入就無謂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">同意請幫推 事關重要</span></span><br />\n我極歡迎非P牌或者名氣大d嘅巴打絲打直接重頭寫過成段再Post過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣rePo咩都好請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink：(22:14開始)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOXpQIMihME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQOXpQIMihME&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=ade5d7c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOXpQIMihME</a>"},{"pid":"78fd37088cf2ebc246d43ccce4b0e1af6fd81e43","tid":1417563,"uid":294715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"65434d63ee6939f16ec91d0506e88aa3298a8bab","tid":1417563,"uid":155107,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"202e77bdd21c6f