,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pFxwNFRHABw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpFxwNFRHABw&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=5cf3a8ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pFxwNFRHABw</a><br />\n大家可睇下，頭條新聞嘅志豪與志森有解釋光復香港時代革命嘅意思<br />\n2：50 開始，4：30 講光復香港嘅意思<br />\n我覺得如果唔想轉口號但又想說服中立民意嘅，好值得參考！"}]}